#: book/templates/book/about.html:18
msgid "About the Author"
msgstr "À propos de l'auteur"

#: book/templates/book/about.html:20
msgid ""
"Coding since age 7. First IT business at 23. MSc in research psychology. "
"Harvard AI certificate. 12+ years building AI and modeling systems."
msgstr ""
"Code depuis l'âge de 7 ans. Premier business IT à 23 ans. Master en "
"psychologie de recherche. Certificat IA de Harvard. 12+ ans à construire des"
" systèmes IA."

#: book/templates/book/about.html:21
msgid ""
"I've watched AI go from academic curiosity to boardroom buzzword. I've built"
" systems that worked and systems that failed. I've seen vendors promise the "
"moon and deliver a rock."
msgstr ""
"J'ai vu l'IA passer de curiosité académique à buzzword de salle de conseil. "
"J'ai construit des systèmes qui marchaient et d'autres qui échouaient. J'ai "
"vu des vendeurs promettre la lune et livrer un caillou."

#: book/templates/book/about.html:22
msgid ""
"This book is what I wish someone had handed me five years ago — a skeptical,"
" practical, deeply researched guide to working with AI without losing your "
"mind or your job."
msgstr ""
"Ce livre est ce que j'aurais aimé qu'on me donne il y a cinq ans — un guide "
"sceptique, pratique et approfondi pour travailler avec l'IA sans perdre la "
"tête ni son emploi."

#: book/templates/book/about.html:23
msgid ""
"I live in South Africa with my partner Donné, daughter Tayla, and four dogs."
" I play tennis and padel. I wear an Apple Watch. I don't have a garden."
msgstr ""
"Je vis en Afrique du Sud avec ma partenaire Donné, ma fille Tayla et quatre "
"chiens. Je joue au tennis et au padel. Je porte une Apple Watch. Je n'ai pas"
" de jardin."

